extends layout

block content
  section.page-hero
    p.eyebrow Help center
    h1 Frequently Asked Questions
    p Answers about shipping, refunds, mystery box contents, accounts, and checkout.
  section.section.faq-list
    article.faq-item
      h2 Is this a real store?
      p No. Mystery Crate Co. is a fake e-commerce website made for a class project. The checkout is mocked and no real payment is processed.
    article.faq-item
      h2 What is inside each mystery box?
      p Each product page explains the theme and gives examples, but the exact items are a surprise.
    article.faq-item
      h2 How does shipping work?
      p In this demo, the checkout form collects a shipping address, but no actual shipping label is created.
    article.faq-item
      h2 What is the refund policy?
      p Because this is a project demo, refunds are not real. A real version would allow refund requests within 30 days if items were damaged or missing.
    article.faq-item
      h2 Do I need an account to buy?
      p You can place a mock order as a guest, but logging in connects the order to your profile purchase history.
    article.faq-item
      h2 What payment information should I enter?
      p Use any 4 or more digits in the mock payment field. Do not enter real card information.
